10 providing short title; defining terms; prohibiting
collection of certain financial records; providing an
11 exception; prohibiting use of certain code to engage
in discriminatory conduct; authorizing the Attorney
12 General to perform certain investigations and provide
notice for violation; providing for violation;
13 prescribing certain remedy for repeated violation;
authorizing Attorney General to enforce provisions of
14 this act; allowing certain defense; providing for
codification; and providing an effective date.
